libgrss - Glib library for feeds
===============================================================================

libgrss is a Glib abstaction to handle feeds in RSS, Atom and other formats.
His code derives from the Liferea feeds reader: http://liferea.sourceforge.net/

REQUIREMENTS
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
libgrss depends on:

  - libxml2 >= 2.7.4
  - libsoup-2.4 >= 2.28.1

INSTALLATION
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
See INSTALL file.

